<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV11">
<l>colliṉāṟṟo ṭarccinī colappaṭumpo ruḷunī</l>
<l>colliṉālco lappaṭātu tōṉṟukiṉṟa cōtinī</l>
<l>colliṉāṟpa ṭaikkanīpa ṭaikkavantu tōṉṟiṉār</l>
<l>colliṉāṟcu ruṅkaniṉku ṇaṅkaḷ colla vallarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are the continuity of the [Vedic] words! You are the meaning expressed [by them]!</l>
<l>You are the light that appears unexpressed by [Vedic] words.</l>
<l>Are people [like Brahmā]—born, being created by You, to create [the worlds]</l>
<l rend="indent">with [the help of the Vedic] words—</l>
<l>[even] capable of succinctly speaking of Your qualities with words?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
